Description: Ege University open data was published in the form of RDF- in accordance with the design issues of linked open data. Therefore- databases which includes data about related systems- were make accessible in the form of RDF using with D2RQ mappings. While RDF mapping we care about to use vocabularies of Linked Universities which aims to create standards that required for linked universities public data on the web. All opened data is accessed the way that addressable and can be queried at SPARQL endpoint.
